reviews.text:
Going through all your recipes, I decided that I wanted to give this one a mix. I was missing FLV blueberry so I made sure to purchase it with my last order. &#xD;
&#xD;
On to the recipe. At first shake, the blueberry was bright and this was coming from the FLV blueberry. After letting it sit for a good week and a half, this recipe is really good. It's creamy and the vanilla note is really nice. The blueberry has pushed it's way to the back and the crumble has come thru with a light coconut note. It's a nice pleasant vape that is very satisfying, not overly sweet, and doesn't kill my tastebuds after vaping it all day. You did a really good job on this recipe! Great use of the flavors you chose and balanced perfectly. Also, thank you for the review you posted on my recipe!
